1
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:35,000
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:39,259
[2005]

3
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,710
The movement is broken.

4
00:01:42,710 --> 00:01:44,110
It can't drive the gears.

5
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,759
Can it be repaired?

6
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,310
I can pay any price.

7
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:49,110
It's not about the money.

8
00:01:49,640 --> 00:01:50,950
It's imported,

9
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:52,070
and it's been discontinued for years.

10
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:53,229
The parts aren't available anymore.

11
00:01:53,229 --> 00:01:54,430
It can't be repaired.

12
00:01:54,509 --> 00:01:55,350
It's not expensive.

13
00:01:55,350 --> 00:01:56,350
Just buy a new one.

14
00:02:00,390 --> 00:02:01,250
Thank you, sir.

15
00:02:04,010 --> 00:02:07,350
[Episode 36: The Gears of Fate]

16
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,280
Xia Xiaolan!

17
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:15,800
I know you're nearby.

18
00:02:16,190 --> 00:02:17,079
Come out!

19
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:20,030
You only play tricks, right?

20
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,730
Do you think I'm scared?

21
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:23,040
I won't lose!

22
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,079
You will never beat me!

23
00:02:25,079 --> 00:02:26,079
Come out!

24
00:02:26,630 --> 00:02:27,400
Come out!

25
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,420
Don't you want to catch me?

26
00:02:29,420 --> 00:02:30,210
Come out!

27
00:02:30,240 --> 00:02:30,870
Come out!

28
00:02:30,340 --> 00:02:33,030
[Shengcheng Commercial Bank]

29
00:02:31,030 --> 00:02:31,470
Ma'am,

30
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:32,280
if you keep making a scene,

31
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,480
I'll call the police.

32
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,660
Du Chengrong's men have left.

33
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,410
Shall we go?

34
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:52,890
Let's go.

35
00:02:57,310 --> 00:02:58,150
Hello.

36
00:02:58,710 --> 00:02:59,970
I have a case to report.

37
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:02,520
The mastermind
behind the wedding banquet poisoning

38
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:05,120
appeared near the old shipyard
in Shengcheng.

39
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:09,750
Xia Ziyu,

40
00:03:10,890 --> 00:03:11,950
you should go back.

41
00:04:04,710 --> 00:04:05,910
Have you got the money ready?

42
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,960
Can you guarantee I'll get to Kong Island?

43
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,630
Will I have a place to stay
when I get there?

44
00:04:09,630 --> 00:04:11,690
Why are you talking so much nonsense?

45
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:13,080
Do you want to go or not?

46
00:04:13,270 --> 00:04:14,630
If not, don't waste time.

47
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:16,560
Many people want to get on the boat.

48
00:04:16,829 --> 00:04:17,240
Jeez.

49
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:18,920
I want to go.

50
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,600
Wait a minute.

51
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,480
Wait for my message tonight.

52
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,680
We'll leave anytime.

53
00:04:57,659 --> 00:05:00,780
[Attack Case on Yunan Province's
Top Science Student]

54
00:05:31,070 --> 00:05:31,870
Xia Xiaolan,

55
00:05:33,230 --> 00:05:34,430
you're finally here.

56
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,240
Young Master!

57
00:05:36,390 --> 00:05:36,920
Here!

58
00:05:46,470 --> 00:05:47,750
Xia Ziyu's parents

59
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:49,240
have been sent to the guesthouse.

60
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,360
But she has a younger brother

61
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,290
named Xia Junbao.

62
00:05:51,290 --> 00:05:52,159
We couldn't find him.

63
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,220
Couldn't find him?

64
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,159
He's a grown man.

65
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,390
How could you not find him?

66
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,630
Xia Junbao has been living in Shengcheng

67
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:57,630
for so many years.

68
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,360
He's very familiar with this place.

69
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,090
I guess someone is helping him.

70
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,070
He's a little kid.

71
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,130
Who would help him?

72
00:06:03,400 --> 00:06:04,070
It must be

73
00:06:04,070 --> 00:06:05,310
Ke Yixiong's men.

74
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:07,950
That loser is really in Shengcheng?

75
00:06:07,950 --> 00:06:08,800
I think so.

76
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:10,360
Xia Ziyu has been keeping him hidden

77
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,760
in Kong Island all along.

78
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:14,240
How many men do we have in Shengcheng?

79
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,240
Call them all out.

80
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:15,950
Young Master,

81
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:16,750
since you said

82
00:06:16,770 --> 00:06:17,920
you wouldn't do anything illegal,

83
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:20,050
they all left to work for other bosses.

84
00:06:21,630 --> 00:06:23,490
How many men does the old man have?

85
00:06:23,560 --> 00:06:24,680
Master only ordered

86
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:25,880
Xia Ziyu to be killed.

87
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:26,560
He doesn't want to get involved

88
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,420
in her business with Xia Xiaolan.

89
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,980
If you come with us now,

90
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:35,020
it can still be considered
turning yourself in.

91
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,450
Turning myself in?

92
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,830
For what?

93
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:43,190
Xia Xiaolan,

94
00:06:43,190 --> 00:06:44,159
this man you chose

95
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,190
is just as naive

96
00:06:47,070 --> 00:06:47,670
as you are.

97
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,320
But I still have to thank you.

98
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:51,870
With your naivety

99
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:53,770
and self-righteousness,

100
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,800
I'm sure you've taken good care

101
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:57,630
of my parents

102
00:06:59,270 --> 00:07:00,530
and my brother, right?

103
00:07:01,120 --> 00:07:02,240
Not very well.

104
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:03,870
But if they are all as

105
00:07:03,870 --> 00:07:04,930
capable as Hongxia

106
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,590
and willing to stay on the right path,

107
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:07,480
at least they can live

108
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:08,280
a normal life.

109
00:07:08,310 --> 00:07:09,480
A normal life?

110
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:14,170
Who doesn't want to live a normal life?

111
00:07:15,390 --> 00:07:17,390
Xia Xiaolan, do you know this place?

112
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:19,510
It was right here

113
00:07:20,480 --> 00:07:21,510
that I lost everything

114
00:07:21,510 --> 00:07:22,800
that belonged to me.

115
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:24,830
My identity,

116
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,070
my name,

117
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,190
my hometown, and my home.

118
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,159
Do you know

119
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:35,120
how I survived 10 years

120
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,560
of living in fear?

121
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:44,270
At that time, I liked the night the most.

122
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:46,870
Because I could stand here

123
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:48,950
and look at the lights across the river.

124
00:07:48,950 --> 00:07:50,190
I looked,

125
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:54,200
while imagining the life
on the other side.

126
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:57,260
I thought as long as
I could make it there,

127
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:59,330
I would live a good life.

128
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,070
But for many years after,

129
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:06,280
I became afraid of the night.

130
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:09,130
I was afraid of the dark.

131
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:13,660
I was afraid of returning to this place.

132
00:08:18,470 --> 00:08:20,070
All of this is because of you.

133
00:08:20,430 --> 00:08:22,760
You are the one
who made me end up like this!

134
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:24,970
Are you done?

135
00:08:29,310 --> 00:08:30,440
After so many years,

136
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,500
you haven't changed a bit.

137
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,530
You still push all the blame

138
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,360
onto others.

139
00:08:37,909 --> 00:08:38,549
Xia Ziyu,

140
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,450
did I make you achieve nothing?

141
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,520
Did I make you lose your dignity?

142
00:08:45,670 --> 00:08:46,630
All of this

143
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,350
started with your jealousy.

144
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,910
You ended up like this

145
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:53,630
because

146
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:55,830
you've always wanted to rely on others.

147
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,720
Cousin,

148
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,600
you are actually very smart.

149
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:04,030
You could have had a better future.

150
00:09:11,030 --> 00:09:11,790
Xia Xiaolan,

151
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,450
do you think you will...

152
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:17,000
have a better future?

153
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,030
Granny Yu.

154
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:24,990
What brings you here?

155
00:09:25,270 --> 00:09:25,600
Granny Yu,

156
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:26,440
I'm here to see Auntie Fen.

157
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,240
Is she at home?

158
00:09:28,550 --> 00:09:30,150
Then you have to wait a while.

159
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:31,600
She hasn't arrived yet.

160
00:09:33,340 --> 00:09:34,340
At this hour?

161
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,510
That's weird.

162
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,120
I know you and your mom

163
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,150
are very close.

164
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:42,040
At such an important moment,

165
00:09:42,670 --> 00:09:44,530
how could she not be here with you?

166
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,240
Go! Go!

167
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:49,110
Xiaolan!

168
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:49,750
Mom!

169
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:50,900
Don't come closer!

170
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:51,890
Or I'll kill her!

171
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,740
Ke Yixiong,

172
00:09:53,220 --> 00:09:54,030
calm down.

173
00:09:57,910 --> 00:09:58,640
Second Aunt.

174
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,150
It's me, Junbao.

175
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,720
Junbao?

176
00:10:03,150 --> 00:10:04,350
You've grown so tall.

177
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:05,840
Why...

178
00:10:06,690 --> 00:10:07,880
Why are you here?

179
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:09,600
Second Aunt,

180
00:10:10,270 --> 00:10:11,440
please help me.

181
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:15,670
I'm not stupid.

182
00:10:16,010 --> 00:10:17,360
When that old man Du Chengrong

183
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:19,090
called me to Shengcheng, I knew

184
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:21,150
I wouldn't be able to go back.

185
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,360
Even without you,

186
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:24,870
he could easily kill me.

187
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:26,270
Xia Ziyu!

188
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:27,690
Let my mom go.

189
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:30,600
And I'll help you
negotiate with Du Chengrong.

190
00:10:32,790 --> 00:10:33,750
How touching.

191
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,080
Negotiate?

192
00:10:38,250 --> 00:10:38,750
I told you that,

193
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:41,000
since I'm here,
it's impossible for me to go back.

194
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:41,670
I came...

195
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:45,000
to settle things with you
once and for all.

196
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:48,650
I know the police are coming soon.

197
00:10:49,630 --> 00:10:51,490
But who are they coming to arrest?

198
00:10:52,510 --> 00:10:53,240
Vivi?

199
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:54,790
Or Xia Ziyu?

200
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:57,080
Xia Xiaolan,

201
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,270
look at my face.

202
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,870
Who should I be?

203
00:11:09,870 --> 00:11:10,600
Who you are

204
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,200
should be up to you.

205
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:15,030
Actually, for me,

206
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:15,910
who I am hasn't mattered

207
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:16,790
for a long time.

208
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:20,200
As long as I can survive,

209
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,670
I can be anyone.

210
00:11:24,270 --> 00:11:25,730
Xia Xiaolan, you're smart

211
00:11:26,550 --> 00:11:27,210
and pretty,

212
00:11:28,510 --> 00:11:31,570
and you've always
gotten the better of me, haven't you?

213
00:11:32,360 --> 00:11:33,870
But I'm Xia Ziyu!

214
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,060
You figured it out a long time ago.

215
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,200
I changed my face,

216
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:40,480
changed my name,

217
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,270
and even

218
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:43,550
changed my dominant hand.

219
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:45,750
But there are many things

220
00:11:45,750 --> 00:11:47,120
I can't forget.

221
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:52,910
I can't forget the child I lost.

222
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:56,390
I can't forget the home I can't return to.

223
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:58,240
Yes,

224
00:12:00,290 --> 00:12:02,670
I'm the one who had someone
break your hand.

225
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:04,870
I'm the one who's always been against you.

226
00:12:04,870 --> 00:12:07,000
I'm the one who had someone poison you!

227
00:12:08,510 --> 00:12:10,710
I just don't want you to have a good life.

228
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,120
I just want you to taste

229
00:12:13,120 --> 00:12:14,450
the feeling of failure.

230
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,640
Come on, Xia Xiaolan.

231
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,030
Beg me.

232
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,320
Kneel and beg me.

233
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,840
Beg me to let your mom go.

234
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:27,240
Kneel.

235
00:12:36,550 --> 00:12:37,400
Xia Ziyu,

236
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:42,920
if I really kneel and beg you,

237
00:12:44,970 --> 00:12:46,030
will you let her go?

238
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,440
Show some sincerity.

239
00:12:59,390 --> 00:13:02,240
Have you ever heard of
"the power of money"?

240
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,270
Are you crazy?

241
00:13:07,720 --> 00:13:08,720
Ke Yixiong, do it!

242
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:12,120
Do it!

243
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,080
What do you mean?

244
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:25,160
Money can't change everything,

245
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:26,820
but it can change a person.

246
00:13:30,200 --> 00:13:31,600
Ke Yixiong, what are you doing?

247
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:32,260
Ke Yixiong!

248
00:13:37,530 --> 00:13:39,280
Second Aunt, I'm Junbao.

249
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,120
Junbao?

250
00:13:41,260 --> 00:13:42,540
You've grown so tall.

251
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:48,090
Second Aunt,

252
00:13:48,240 --> 00:13:49,360
please help me.

253
00:13:57,850 --> 00:13:58,510
He fainted.

254
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,400
What's going on here?

255
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:04,180
Mr. Liu,

256
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,710
this is Ke Yixiong.

257
00:14:05,710 --> 00:14:07,220
We finally caught this guy.

258
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:07,750
Mrs. Liu,

259
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:09,320
we need to cooperate with Xiaolan

260
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:10,380
and finish the act.

261
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,410
Where is Junbao?

262
00:14:25,030 --> 00:14:26,080
Xia Xiaolan

263
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:28,160
really underestimated me.

264
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,570
Trying to buy me off with money?

265
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:32,820
Let me tell you,

266
00:14:33,720 --> 00:14:35,480
I just want to kill Xia Xiaolan.

267
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,780
Unfortunately, your plan

268
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:39,610
has failed.

269
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:48,270
I advise you

270
00:14:49,250 --> 00:14:50,780
to think it over carefully.

271
00:15:01,440 --> 00:15:02,100
Zhang Qing.

272
00:15:03,630 --> 00:15:05,490
He took Du Chengrong's territory

273
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,090
and died in a traffic accident.

274
00:15:09,510 --> 00:15:10,170
Xu Chengye.

275
00:15:10,670 --> 00:15:12,270
He took Du Chengrong's woman

276
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:14,120
and disappeared 2 months later.

277
00:15:14,270 --> 00:15:15,000
Wu Tianhao.

278
00:15:15,440 --> 00:15:17,640
He didn't follow Du Chengrong's orders

279
00:15:17,840 --> 00:15:19,370
and accidentally drowned.

280
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:21,600
What do you mean?

281
00:15:22,550 --> 00:15:24,670
When Du Chengrong asked Xia Ziyu
to come back,

282
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:26,860
he never intended for her to return alive.

283
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:27,590
Helping her?

284
00:15:28,620 --> 00:15:29,240
Have you ever thought about

285
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,900
how she has been treating you?

286
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,640
If you cooperate with us,

287
00:15:39,150 --> 00:15:40,080
finish this act,

288
00:15:41,030 --> 00:15:42,790
and turn yourself in to the police,

289
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:44,390
you'll at least have a chance

290
